'''Succession pools''' were integral parts of [[damutek]]s. They were self-contained bodies of water that stored the [[Heart/Legends|heart]], [[Lung/Legends|lungs]], and [[Liver/Legends|livers]] of most [[Yuuzhan Vong]] beings. They were also used as waste disposal systems, which would absorb the nutrients from the waste to nourish the damutek.

When the Yuuzhan Vong conquered [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] and [[Terraforming/Legends|Vongformed]] the planet into [[Coruscant/Legends#Yuuzhan'tar|Yuuzhan'tar]], the [[Great Western Sea/Legends|Western Sea]] became a giant succession pool.

